'''Kelly Long''' is an Irish actress.&lt;ref&gt;http://www.thefilmlobby.com/users/77&lt;/ref&gt; She portrays [[Joyeuse Erenford]], [[Walder Frey]]'s eighth wife, in the [[Season 1|first season]] episode &quot;[[Baelor]]&quot; and the [[Season 3|third season]] episode &quot;[[The Rains of Castamere (episode)|The Rains of Castamere]]&quot;. She also works as a stand-in for [[Emilia Clarke]], [[Michelle Fairley]], [[Lena Headey]], and [[Sophie Turner]]. In Season 2, Long began working full-time for ''Game of Thrones'' art department.&lt;ref&gt;http://www.thetimewarriors.co.uk/blog/?p=8002&lt;/ref&gt;

